value.string: Get policy number from the input file and login into the horison and indentifies which senario the policy falls (cancelled policy,contains y or not) and perform the respective actions and update the corresponding status in the input file itself.
1. Get each policy from the input file and login into the horison.
2. If policy is cancelled policy, then notate horison as cancelled policy and come out of horison. Update status and comments as cancelled policy in the input excel sheet.
3. If policy is already removed, then notate horison as no items to remove and come out of horison. Update status and comments as already removed policy in the input excel sheet.

4. If policy has items to remove, then compare items with the horison and excel if matches purge it and notate horison with the before and after premium amount and come out of horison. Update status and comments as complete in the input excel sheet.
